chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
yes
cool! i see a twig on my left leading to a small island with a tiger
don't know where to go next, any ideas?
cross the stream
Vale, oficialmente en la isla del tigre.
Es algo lindo, desde una distancia segura. ¿que sigue?
there is a parrot on a tree go around it
alright, avoiding the parrot
now, what's the next move?
there are three rocks going across a stream cross it towards a frog
alright, hopped across those rocks, chillin' near the frog now
what's our next move?
move towards the tail fo the alligator and walk across its back to the island at its mouth
yikes! managed to get across that alligator's back, safe and sound on the island now
go to the two rocks that cross the stream it is by the elephan
Entendido, estoy junto al elefante ahora
¿que sigue?
cross them by the giraffe
Muy bien, acabo de pasar junto a la jirafa.
¿que sigue?
walk across a stick under a tree with a snake in it
made
I went under the tree with the snake - eek
ahead there should be the treasure
¡ajá, ya lo veo! Acabo de atrapar el tesoro
gracias por guiarme! *finalizado*
hola, q tal? ready to go?
ready
great! first, walk a few steps west till you reach a trail under a wooden bench
you'll see a florist stand nearby
ok
Justo antes de llegar al puesto de floristería, gire en U bruscamente a la izquierda.
ok
Ahora, vuelve a cruzar el sendero hacia el perro blanco.
oki
all right, now move south over the branch, and keep heading southwards
there's another white dog waiting for you there
ok
once there, continue in that direction
you'll stumble upon a mat with a bowl of berries. keep moving west
okay
Verás una rama de madera cruzando un río, llévala hacia el norte.
will do
after crossing the river, you'll see a green bush
go clockwise around it, but don't touch it!
got it
good job! now, walk till you reach the florist stand
im there
¡impresionante! Ahora gira a la izquierda y pasa por debajo de la tribuna hacia un gran puente con dos personas en bicicleta.
do i cross the bridge
nope, just pass by on the west, mate
ok what now
Justo después del puente, verás a dos ancianos encantadores sentados en un banco con sus periódicos.
camina unos pasos hacia el sur desde ellos
OK
Verás otra rama de madera y un arbusto verde, camina entre ellos.
OK
ahora, ve hacia el este entre la rama y el arbusto.
¡Unos pocos pasos y listo!
ok
there's a young brown deer near you
you've reached the final spot. well done, mate!
hey, estas listo?
reasdy
¡dulce! Estoy en la tienda en el norte.
¿Adónde debería dirigirme?
go south until you see a bush with a dog, go on the west side of the bush
ok cool, i see the dog
está sentado al lado del fuego. ¿debo continuar al sur o tomar otro camino?
moving east go north around the fire then south under some tall mushrooms
Muy bien, ahora veo el hongo rojo.
hacia el sur, supongo
go towards the blue car
got it, i'm by the blue car
which way to go now?
now take the brown trail west then south at the first south turn
following the brown route
to the south. I see a blue telescope, is this the right place?
yes go south of the telescope
ok cool, now i'm standing directly south of the telescope
walk the trail east until you see the pile of rocks at the base of the hill
awesome, i'm at the rocks
i see a wooden house next to them. is this the end of our trail?
yes climb up the rocks next to the house
Genial, ahora voy a subir por las rocas.
He llegado a la casa. *finalizado*
hola, q tal? ready to play?
ready amigo
awesome! first, swing underneath the first palm tree we're near and trot on towards the second tree
then, make a sudden left before you reach the third tree. got it?
got it
perfect! now keep strolling south for a bit
you're doing really well!
ok
next thing: just hang a left around that brown puppy you see, and then drift right heading south again
cool?
ok
nice! now aim for that spot between the big rock to your left and the small one to your right
it'll lead you straight to the water
at the water now
¡excelente! Ahora prepárate para conocer a nuestro amigo malhumorado.
Sumérgete en el agua y saluda al gran cangrejo rojo, luego gira a la derecha, haciendo compañía a esa gran roca en el lado izquierdo.
at the red crab now what
perfecto! now, stay nice and tight to that big rock and just keep on truckin' west through the water, okay?
how far
just until you swim past a medium-sized rock. then, you should spot a shark in the water
partnership the shark a safe distance to your right. any questions?
do i go close to the shark
nope, no need
make a major right turn before you get too close. safe is the name of the game here, amigo!
do i go back on land
¡Sí, buena decisión! Dispara a ese espacio entre la roca mediana y la pelota con esas franjas azules, amarillas y blancas.
Una vez que estés fuera del agua, sigue caminando hacia el norte, ¿vale?
im in between the rock and the ball
great work, mate! now, tilt a bit to the left and keep going northwest
you're looking for a gap between a red tent and a giant speaker
im between them
good job! now imagine you are a painter and draw an arc around the tent
it's fun, isn't it?
im on the other side of the tent
excelente amigo! Ahora, tómate un respiro y dirígete hacia el sur, pero detente justo antes de volver a tocar el agua.
im right before the water
¡Frío! Ahora gira a la derecha y corre debajo de ese kayak rojo.
¡Ah, y cuidado con la cabeza!
done
¡as! Ahora gire bruscamente a la derecha y camine hacia el norte junto al kayak.
¿listo?
there
fantastic! look out for a small green bush
you've made it buddy!
